        .grs__bottom
          a.grs__link.linkedin-link(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/artsvuni" target="_blank") Linkedin
          a.grs__link(href="mailto:alexander@artsvuni.com" target="_blank") Get in touch

      .width-wrapper_black
        .bps.bps_padding-bottom-0
          .content-block
            h1.title Farfetch.com <br/>Navigation
            p.bps__paragraph.accent-text On joining Farfetch in 2016, my first project was to redesign the navigation across both desktop and mobile.
          .bps__browser-preview__desktop
            video(controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata")
              source(src="./video/browser-home-desktop.mp4" type="video/mp4")
            img(src="./images/navigation-slide-browser.png")
          .bps__browser-preview__mobile
            video(controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata")
              source(src="./video/browser-home-mobile.mp4" type="video/mp4")
            img(src="./images/navigation-slide-browser-mobile.png")

      .width-wrapper_gray
        .pps
          .phone
            .phone-preview
              video.phone-preview__video( controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata" )
                source(src="./video/ios-app-home.mp4" type="video/mp4")
              img.phone-preview__frame(srcset="./images/iphone-frame.png 2x")
          .content-wrap
            .content-block
              h1.title Home view for iOS/Android
              p.accent-text Working to improve engagement, I started focusing on native application design. <br/>I eventually created a specialist mobile app design team at Farfetch.
      
      .pps.pps_reverse
        .phone
          .phone-preview
            img.phone-preview__image(srcset="./images/search-and-navigation.png 2x")
            img.phone-preview__frame(srcset="./images/iphone-frame.png 2x")
        .content-wrap
          .content-block
            h1.title Search and navigation
            p.accent-text Over 2 years my team and I led the effort focused on iterative improvements of Farfetch mobile apps.

      .width-wrapper_gray.width-wrapper_overflow-hidden
        .uips
          .content-block
              h1.title Component driven design
              p.accent-text To improve alignment and consistency, I built a technical design practice based on close collaboration between the design and engineering teams.
          img.uips__preview_desktop(src="./images/ui-kit-preview-desktop.png")
          img.uips__preview_mobile(src="./images/ui-kit-preview-mobile.png")

      .pps
        .phone
          .phone-preview
            video.phone-preview__video( controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata" )
              source(src="./video/ios-app-inputs.mp4" type="video/mp4")
            img.phone-preview__frame(srcset="./images/iphone-frame.png 2x")
        .content-wrap
          .content-block
            h1.title Accessible inputs
            p.accent-text Looking closer at micro-interactions to improve usability, I led the initiative to make our native apps more inclusive and accessible.
      
      .width-wrapper_gray
        .pps.pps_reverse
          .phone
            .phone-preview
              video.phone-preview__video( controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata" )
                source(src="./video/ios-app-localisation.mp4" type="video/mp4")
              img.phone-preview__frame(srcset="./images/iphone-frame.png 2x")
          .content-wrap
            .content-block
              h1.title International localisation
              p.accent-text As Farfetch expanded to new markets, I was responsible for optimising our native interfaces to work equally well in all languages.
      
      .pps
        .phone
          .phone-preview
            video.phone-preview__video( controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata" )
              source(src="./video/ios-china-app.mp4" type="video/mp4")
            img.phone-preview__frame(srcset="./images/iphone-frame.png 2x")
        .content-wrap
          .content-block
            h1.title Farfetch <br/> China app
            p.accent-text As a principal designer, I led our Shanghai-based design team to create and launch a localised version of the Farfetch app in 2018.
      
      .width-wrapper_gray
        .bps
          .content-block.desk-margin-top-l
            h1.title Accessible prototyping kit
            p.bps__paragraph.accent-text I defined design standards for the native app and developed toolkits to help designers ensure that Farfetch interfaces are always AA accessible.
          video.bps__video_desktop(controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata")
            source(src="./video/dynamictype-desktop.mp4" type="video/mp4")
          video.bps__video_mobile(controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata")
            source(src="./video/dynamictype-mobile.mp4" type="video/mp4")
      
      .width-wrapper_black
        .bps.bps_black
          .content-block
            h1.title Native UI <br/>framework
            p.bps__paragraph.accent-text I teamed up with principal engineer Fabio Almeida to create a framework for designing and building production level interfaces faster than ever before.
          video.bps__video_desktop(controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata")
            source(src="./video/ui-framework.mp4" type="video/mp4")
          video.bps__video_mobile(controls=false playsinline autoplay muted loop preload="metadata")
            source(src="./video/ui-framework-mobile.mp4" type="video/mp4")
      
